<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:08:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>埃及新内阁宣誓就职，日益严峻的经济挑战引发公众不满</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/egypt-swears-in-a-new-cabinet-as-mounting-economic-challenges-fuel-public-discontent/00000190-789f-d7ff-a7b2-fbbf501b0000</link><description>由总理穆斯塔法·马德布利担任主席的新内阁包括重大变化，特别是在国防和经济相关的投资组合方面</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/egypt-swears-in-a-new-cabinet-as-mounting-economic-challenges-fuel-public-discontent/00000190-789f-d7ff-a7b2-fbbf501b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部购物中心发生刺伤袭击，造成一人死亡、一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-another-seriously-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-in-northern-israeli-shopping-mall/00000190-7852-d7ff-a7b2-fbf243dd0000</link><description>警方报告称，行凶者是阿拉伯小镇纳哈夫的一名以色列居民；家人在流传的视频中认出了他的身份后赶到。三人都被戴上手铐，他的兄弟也被绑在腿上，眼睛也被蒙住</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:12:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/one-killed-another-seriously-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-in-northern-israeli-shopping-mall/00000190-7852-d7ff-a7b2-fbf243dd0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管发生了战争，以色列初创公司在第二季度筹集了更多资金。所有其他消息都是坏消息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-israeli-startups-raised-more-money-all-the-other-news-is-bad/00000190-7868-de25-a3df-7cfbd8900000</link><description>以色列初创公司第二季度筹集了更多资金，但该行业仍处于低迷状态，无处可求助</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:51:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-israeli-startups-raised-more-money-all-the-other-news-is-bad/00000190-7868-de25-a3df-7cfbd8900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸定居点预建 6,000 多套住房</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-advances-over-6-000-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/00000190-7828-d8da-aff3-7f6bc9430000</link><description>上周，财政部长斯莫特里奇宣布政府批准旨在“反对承认巴勒斯坦国”的措施，其中包括授权建造数千套住房并将西岸五个未经授权的前哨基地合法化</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:48:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-advances-over-6-000-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/00000190-7828-d8da-aff3-7f6bc9430000</guid></item><item><title>WZO 批准在赫茨尔墓地举行纪念米里亚姆·阿德尔森的活动，并关闭了公共广场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/wzo-allows-event-honoring-miriam-adelson-at-herzl-burial-site-shutting-down-public-plaza/00000190-77a3-d705-a7f5-fffba9fc0000</link><description>世界犹太复国主义组织主席在没有与该组织领导层讨论该问题的情况下批准了该活动。 WZO 副主席表示，我们不会授权这样做，将其交给慈善家是一个严重的错误。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:55:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/wzo-allows-event-honoring-miriam-adelson-at-herzl-burial-site-shutting-down-public-plaza/00000190-77a3-d705-a7f5-fffba9fc0000</guid></item><item><title>罕见的老式以色列演出海报收藏唤起了数十年的音乐记忆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rare-vintage-israeli-gigs-posters-collection-conjures-decades-of-music-memories/00000190-7325-d0bf-a9fd-77fff80c0000</link><description>两名以色列音乐和纪念品爱好者在档案、工具棚、公寓和集装箱中筛选，寻找以色列音乐演出海报。结果在一本新书中呈现</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:01:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/rare-vintage-israeli-gigs-posters-collection-conjures-decades-of-music-memories/00000190-7325-d0bf-a9fd-77fff80c0000</guid></item><item><title>新的哥伦比亚大学管理人员文本显示，院长们讨论犹太学生的“特权”和“$$$$”，并抨击希勒尔领导人是“问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/new-columbia-administrator-texts-show-deans-talking-jewish-student-privilege-and/00000190-77d3-d2ab-a7d2-77ffef080000</link><description>虽然短信的内容之前已经报道过，但完整的交流显示，大学官员淡化了学生对反犹太主义的担忧，猛烈抨击了学校校长希勒尔，并暗示犹太学生因为金钱而受到关注</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/new-columbia-administrator-texts-show-deans-talking-jewish-student-privilege-and/00000190-77d3-d2ab-a7d2-77ffef080000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗总统候选人在周五决选前讨论核协议和经济制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/irans-presidential-hopefuls-talk-nuclear-deal-economic-sanctions-ahead-of-friday-runoff/00000190-7772-d705-a7f5-fffb67450000</link><description>伊朗改革派候选人表示，他将努力恢复与世界大国的核协议，而他的强硬派竞争对手则谴责他没有任何计划取消西方国家实施的经济制裁</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:41:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/irans-presidential-hopefuls-talk-nuclear-deal-economic-sanctions-ahead-of-friday-runoff/00000190-7772-d705-a7f5-fffb67450000</guid></item><item><title>定居者在约旦河西岸前哨撤离时与以色列军队发生冲突，投掷燃烧弹和石块</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/settlers-clash-with-israeli-forces-at-west-bank-outpost-throw-firebombs-stones/00000190-773a-de25-a3df-7fbbabd70000</link><description>前哨站的定居者点燃轮胎，向以色列军队投掷石块，以撤离巴勒斯坦私人土地上的建筑，该建筑已经存在了两年但没有得到执行。一名国防官员证实恐怖袭击源自前哨基地，并获得政府批准撤离</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 06:53:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/settlers-clash-with-israeli-forces-at-west-bank-outpost-throw-firebombs-stones/00000190-773a-de25-a3df-7fbbabd70000</guid></item><item><title>在每天接二连三的丑闻之下，内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们转移了人们对以色列不断升级的危机的注意力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-disaster-a-day-government-diverts-attention-away-from-israels-dire-situation/00000190-751c-d705-a7f5-fdff39230000</link><description>希法医院院长获释、加沙电力以及《纽约时报》的一篇报道对以色列人来说没有什么新鲜事：部长们制造并夸大丑闻，希望公众忘记他们持续的失败。政客和他们派往战场的士兵之间的鸿沟从未如此之大</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 03:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-disaster-a-day-government-diverts-attention-away-from-israels-dire-situation/00000190-751c-d705-a7f5-fdff39230000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩真主党高级战地指挥官在以色列无人机袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-targeted-terror-cell-in-west-bank-drone-strike-palestinians-four-killed/00000190-764d-d6e9-afb6-777d76dc0000</link><description>以色列警方证实，被枪杀的袭击者是以色列的阿拉伯公民 ■ 加兰特表示，以色列更愿意在黎巴嫩达成协议，但如有必要，将与真主党作战 ■ 白宫官员：拜登“可能”本月在华盛顿会见内塔尼亚胡 ■ 定居者投掷非法前哨撤离后，以色列军队遭到石块和燃烧弹袭击 ■ 黎巴嫩发射火箭弹后，以色列国防军袭击真主党目标 ■ 马克龙敦促内塔尼亚胡避免黎巴嫩爆发全面战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-03/ty-article-live/idf-says-it-targeted-terror-cell-in-west-bank-drone-strike-palestinians-four-killed/00000190-764d-d6e9-afb6-777d76dc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阿拉伯社区数小时内有两人被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-people-shot-and-killed-within-hours-in-israels-arab-community/00000190-7501-d0bf-a9fd-75fbff820000</link><description>周二晚上，一名 15 岁少年也被枪杀 ■ 《国土报》的统计显示，自 2023 年初以来，以色列阿拉伯社区已发生 111 起凶杀案</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/two-people-shot-and-killed-within-hours-in-israels-arab-community/00000190-7501-d0bf-a9fd-75fbff820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卫生部扣留了在抗议中被拘留的医生的“良好信誉证明”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/health-ministry-withholds-certificate-from-doctor-who-was-detained-at-protest/00000190-74c7-d705-a7f5-fcfff8e50000</link><description>Daphna Shochat 博士在 6 月的一次反政府集会上被拘留，后被无罪释放。即将移居英国的肖查特向卫生部申请了证明，以便她能找到工作。她被拒绝并被告知她有犯罪记录，但警方否认了这一点</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:40:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/health-ministry-withholds-certificate-from-doctor-who-was-detained-at-protest/00000190-74c7-d705-a7f5-fcfff8e50000</guid></item><item><title>一场毁灭性的言论席卷了以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/an-annihilation-discourse-has-taken-over-israel/00000190-735c-d0bf-a9fd-77fe9eda0000</link><description>历史学家本尼·莫里斯和许多其他人（包括左翼人士）呼吁以色列对伊朗发动核攻击，这是毁灭一切的复仇战略的延续。我们必须趁我们还可以的时候走上街头抗议</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:05:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/an-annihilation-discourse-has-taken-over-israel/00000190-735c-d0bf-a9fd-77fe9eda0000</guid></item><item><title>26 张标志性照片讲述以色列的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/understanding-israel-through-iconic-photos-taken-before-and-after-its-establishment/00000190-73e9-d705-a7f5-fbfb976c0000</link><description>从 1948 年毁灭性的恐怖袭击到本·古里安倒立，特拉维夫博物馆展示了 27 张创造历史的标志性照片</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 19:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/understanding-israel-through-iconic-photos-taken-before-and-after-its-establishment/00000190-73e9-d705-a7f5-fbfb976c0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国、俄罗斯、伊朗和以色列政府在拜登辩论失败后幸灾乐祸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/why-china-russia-iran-and-israels-government-are-gloating-after-bidens-debate-debacle/00000190-73d7-d129-afba-fff7ac9c0000</link><description>敌人欢欣鼓舞，盟友焦虑：全球对乔·拜登表现和连任机会的大量报道反映了 11 月选举的巨大利害关系 — — 从美利坚共和国的未来到世界秩序本身</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 18:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/why-china-russia-iran-and-israels-government-are-gloating-after-bidens-debate-debacle/00000190-73d7-d129-afba-fff7ac9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长声称推翻大屠杀纪念馆主席的背后有“很多原因”，但没有引用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-says-many-reasons-to-oust-yad-vashem-chair-but-doesnt-cite-them/00000190-7442-d7a4-a9dc-ff7b631d0000</link><description>一份信息自由请求显示，约夫·基什部长的办公室只收到一封投诉信，其中没有像部长所声称的那样提出不当行为或虐待行为。该投诉是由一家美国组织在 Yad Vashem 因纠纷与该组织断绝关系后发出的</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:28:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-says-many-reasons-to-oust-yad-vashem-chair-but-doesnt-cite-them/00000190-7442-d7a4-a9dc-ff7b631d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 270 天：真主党副领袖表示加沙休战是停火的唯一途径</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-270-hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-gaza-truce-only-path-to-cease-fire/00000190-745b-de25-a3df-7cfb14400000</link><description>据《纽约时报》报道，以色列国防军高级将领寻求在加沙停火，即使这会让哈马斯暂时掌权。 ■ 10 月 7 日被杀和绑架的以色列国防军观察员的父母发誓，将继续战斗，直到针对大屠杀事件成立国家调查委员会 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府选择法官接替前首席大法官阿哈伦·巴拉克 (Aharon Barak) 在国际法院代表政府 ■ 战争结束 270 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-270-hezbollah-deputy-chief-says-gaza-truce-only-path-to-cease-fire/00000190-745b-de25-a3df-7cfb14400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列真的想被指控在加沙犯下更多战争罪吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-02/ty-article/.highlight/does-israel-actually-want-to-be-accused-of-more-war-crimes-in-gaza/00000190-73d7-dbfd-a5d1-f3d7f1ab0000</link><description>在看起来像是犯罪意图的竞争中，以色列政治人物坚持提倡折磨巴勒斯坦平民的政策，似乎是为了证明他们违反国际法的承诺</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:38:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-02/ty-article/.highlight/does-israel-actually-want-to-be-accused-of-more-war-crimes-in-gaza/00000190-73d7-dbfd-a5d1-f3d7f1ab0000</guid></item><item><title>“是时候再给和平一次机会了”：数千人聚集在特拉维夫参加以色列-巴勒斯坦和平会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-time-to-give-peace-another-chance-thousands-gather-at-peace-conference-in-tel-aviv/00000190-73b5-d705-a7f5-fbff44db0000</link><description>在一场题为“是时候了：伟大的和平会议”的活动中，在以色列人和巴勒斯坦人最黑暗的时期，竞技场上充满了对未来的希望。一位巴勒斯坦发言者说，“这个家园正在流血，如果我们现在不阻止，我们都将走上集体自杀的道路”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-time-to-give-peace-another-chance-thousands-gather-at-peace-conference-in-tel-aviv/00000190-73b5-d705-a7f5-fbff44db0000</guid></item></channel></rss>